  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(* Coefficient matrices C0,C1,C2 with t2[λ1,λ2][1,1][u] = C0 + C1 u + C2 u^2.\n   Extracted entrywise via CoefficientList in a dummy variable (NOT by evaluating at numeric\n   points). Memoized per (λ1,λ2) — reusable across all (M,n) of that representation. *)\nClearAll[t2Coeffs];\nt2Coeffs[λ1_, λ2_] := t2Coeffs[λ1, λ2] = Module[{uu, mat, cl},\n   mat = t2[λ1, λ2][1, 1][uu];\n   cl = Map[PadRight[CoefficientList[#, uu], 3] &, mat, {2}];\n   Table[cl[[All, All, k]], {k, 1, 3}]\n];\n(* check: C2 must equal (κ1+κ2) Id — leading-order asymptotics match τ by construction *)\nWith[{Cs = t2Coeffs[1, 1]}, \"max|C2-(κ1+κ2)Id|\" -> Max[Abs[Flatten[Cs[[3]] - (κ1 + κ2) IdentityMatrix[4]]]]]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"352966\" data-output-id=\"32\" data-out-n=\"223\" data-sub-idx=\"4\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"29\" data-sub-start=\"10\" data-sub-end=\"10\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[223]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrnhekfd-xquyfdv\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"XHRleHR7bWF4fEMyLSgkXGthcHBhJDErJFxrYXBwYSQyKUlkfH1cdG8gMC5cdGltZXMgMTBeey0yOX0=\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">max|C2-(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">κ</span><span class=\"mord\">1+</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">κ</span><span class=\"mord\">2)Id|</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0.</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">×</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8641em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8641em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">−</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">29</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[223]= \\text{max|C2-($\\kappa$1+$\\kappa$2)Id|}\\to 0.\\times 10^{-29}",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
