      {
       "data": "SoVFact::mu: μEff=c/cPred ≠ 1 for (λ1,λ2,s1)=(1,1,1): μEff=-0.809524 (site-2 passthrough not identity — a finding, not a failure).\nSoVFact::mu: μEff=c/cPred ≠ 1 for (λ1,λ2,s1)=(1,2,1): μEff=-1.80952 (site-2 passthrough not identity — a finding, not a failure).\nSoVFact::mu: μEff=c/cPred ≠ 1 for (λ1,λ2,s1)=(1,3,1): μEff=-2.80952 (site-2 passthrough not identity — a finding, not a failure).\nGeneral::stop: Further output of SoVFact::mu will be suppressed during this calculation.",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      },
      {
       "data": "{\n\t\"name\": \"WolframKernelMessage\",\n\t\"message\": \"SoVFact::mu: μEff=c/cPred ≠ 1 for (λ1,λ2,s1)=(1,1,1): μEff=-0.809524 (site-2 passthrough not identity — a finding, not a failure).\\nSoVFact::mu: μEff=c/cPred ≠ 1 for (λ1,λ2,s1)=(1,2,1): μEff=-1.80952 (site-2 passthrough not identity — a finding, not a failure).\\nSoVFact::mu: μEff=c/cPred ≠ 1 for (λ1,λ2,s1)=(1,3,1): μEff=-2.80952 (site-2 passthrough not identity — a finding, not a failure).\\nGeneral::stop: Further output of SoVFact::mu will be suppressed during this calculation.\",\n\t\"stack\": \"\"\n}",
